ommunity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%E2%80%99s%20terms%20of%20service%20state%20the%20platform%20does%20not%20allow%20videos%20%E2%80%9Cshowing%20or%20promoting%20disordered%20eating%20or%20any%20dangerous%20weight%20loss%20behaviors.%26quot%3B%20TikTok%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20take%20the%20trends%20most%20seriously%20are%20at%20greater%20risk%20of%20subscribing%20to%20some%20of%20the%20more%20controversial%20ideas%20linked%20to%20looksmaxxing%2C%20Shami%20said%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincel-forum-members-post-rape-every-29-minutes-ccdh-study-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincel%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20trollish%20behavior%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20tragic%20results.%20The%20slang%20term%20%E2%80%9Cropemaxxing%2C%E2%80%9D%20for%20example%2C%20means%20pushing%20someone%20to%20suicide%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Creborn%E2%80%9D%20as%20less%20ugly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20say%20on%20TikTok%20so%20far%20it%20is%20more%20like%20a%20satire%2C%20kind%20of%20jokey%20thing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shami%20said.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20own%20popular%20videos%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20on%20%E2%80%9Cday%2013%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CJordan%20Barrett%20diet%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20consisted%20of%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20oxygen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarvemaxxing%2C%20in%20Shami%E2%80%99s%20opinion%2C%20is%20real%2C%20but%20isn%E2%80%99t%20as%20intense%20as%20it%20sounds.%20%E2%80%9CStarvemaxxing%20isn't%20actually%20starving%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20means%20you're%20cutting%20down%20in%20attempts%20to%20reach%20a%20very%20low%20body%20fat%20percentage%20to%20look%20better%20in%20the%20face.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kareem%20Shami%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cf7d51a610a9069d59c97c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKareem%20Shami%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20looksmaxxing%20creators%20on%20TikTok%20with%201.5%20million%20followers.%3Cp%3E%40syrianpsycho%2FTikTok%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20users%20on%20looksmaxxing%20forums%20say%20they%20eat%20as%20little%20as%20possible%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20having%20an%20angular%20appearance%20like%20Lachowski.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20looksmaxxer%20subreddit%2C%20a%20user%20asked%20in%20December%202023%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20many%20calories%20do%20you%20guys%20eat%20a%20day%20for%20more%20hollow%20cheeks%20and%20how%20often%20do%20you%20starvemaxx%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C1500%20calories%20a%20day%20max%2C%E2%80%9D%20another%20user%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20another%20looksmaxxer%20forum%20dated%20April%202023%2C%20a%20user%20said%20they%20%E2%80%9Cneed%20help%E2%80%9D%20with%20starvemaxxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeen%20making%20myself%20throw%20up%20after%20meals%20that%20are%20too%20heavy%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20wrote.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20tips%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20food%20even%20more%20please%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20post%20from%20July%202022%20saw%20a%20user%20describe%20a%20day%20in%20their%20starvemaxxing%20schedule%3A%20one%20cup%20of%20Special%20K%20cereal%2C%20one%20protein%20shake%2C%20one%20packet%20of%20butter%20popcorn%2C%20and%20one%20cup%20of%20salmon%20with%20soy%20sauce%2C%20totaling%201%2C300%20calories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20calorie%20requirements%20vary%20from%20person%20to%20person%20depending%20on%20factors%20including%20their%20body%20size%2C%20activity%20levels%2C%20and%20genetics%2C%20to%20put%20this%20into%20context%3A%20a%20four-year-old%20boy%20is%20estimated%20to%20require%201%2C386%20calories%20a%20day%2C%20while%20an%20average%2018-year-old%20needs%203%2C155%2C%20according%20to%20the%20British%20Nutrition%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPediatric%20dietitian%20Clare%20Thornton-Wood%20told%20BI%20that%20starvemaxxing%20sounds%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20unwise%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20fasting%20or%20dieting%20is%20a%20dangerous%20practice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20being%20risky%2C%20their%20efforts%20are%20likely%20in%20vain.%20While%20cutting%20calories%20extremely%20low%20may%20lead%20to%20fat%20loss%20anywhere%20on%20the%20body%2C%20including%20the%20face%2C%20genetics%20play%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20someone%E2%80%99s%20facial%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20real%20way%20to%20verify%20whether%20people%20claiming%20to%20eat%20extremely%20little%20are%20telling%20the%20truth%20or%20exaggerating%20for%20attention%2C%20Elizabeth%20Daniels%2C%20a%20professor%20and%20director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Appearance%20Research%20at%20the%20University%20of%20the%20West%20of%20England%2C%20UK%2C%20who%20specializes%20in%20body%20image%20issues%20among%20young%20people%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etold%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20believes%20such%20trends%20are%20still%20concerning%20given%20that%20younger%20social%20media%20users%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20discern%20jokes%20from%20reality.%20Even%20if%20a%20handful%20of%20boys%20are%20starving%20themselves%2C%20that%20could%20have%20serious%20consequences%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohan%20Drumev%2C%20who%20is%2019%20and%20lives%20in%20Dubai%2C%20is%20another%20looksmaxxing%20creator%2C%20with%20around%2056%2C000%20TikTok%20followers.%20He%20has%20a%20similar%20look%20to%20Shami%2C%20with%20dark%20hair%20and%20eyes%20and%20angular%20facial%20features.%20He%20also%20shares%20his%20transformation%20from%20the%20fresh-faced%20teen%20he%20was%20at%20school%20to%20an%20intense-gazed%2C%20muscular%20young%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20BI%2C%20Drumev%20agreed%20with%20Shami%20that%20starvemaxxing%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmostly%20a%20joke%2C%E2%80%9D%20but%20said%20some%20do%20take%20part%20in%20it%20to%20%E2%80%9Close%20lots%20of%20weight%20rapidly%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cachieve%20a%20lean%20physique%20or%20hollow%20cheeks%20for%20a%20more%20modelesque%20look.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20can%20be%20bad%20because%20the%20looksmaxxing%20community%20has%20lots%20of%20young%20teenagers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20some%20of%20them%20might%20actually%20take%20it%20seriously%20and%20starve%20themselves%20and%20ruin%20their%20health%20or%20just%20their%20potential%20to%20actually%20become%20more%20attractive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Johan%20Drumev%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cf7c43f533b039a8847dce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohan%20Drumev%20is%20a%20looksmaxxing%20TikToker%20with%2056%2C000%20followers.%3Cp%3EJohan%20Drumev%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELachowski%2C%20who%20has%20two%20young%20sons%2C%20said%20it%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdisheartening%20and%20concerning%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20starvemaxxing%2C%20as%20he%20encourages%20all%20his%20fans%2C%20including%20junior%20models%2C%20to%20prioritize%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%20with%20balance%20and%20self-care%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20deeply%20saddened%20to%20hear%20that%20my%20work%20has%20inadvertently%20influenced%20such%20unhealthy%20behaviors%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lachowski%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYoung%20men%20are%20becoming%20more%20body-conscious%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20unclear%20why%20looksmaxxing%20has%20suddenly%20become%20popular.%20But%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20public%20consciousness%20focused%20on%20body%20image%20issues%20among%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20Daniels%20said.%20The%20rise%20of%20looksmaxxing%20and%20starvemaxxing%20could%20reflect%20how%20such%20concerns%20are%20on%20the%20rise%20among%20young%20men%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%202023%20report%20by%20the%20UK%20government%2C%20for%20example%2C%20found%20that%2028%25%20of%20men%20surveyed%20had%20felt%20anxious%20about%20how%20their%20bodies%20looked%2C%20while%20another%20report%20from%202022%20by%20University%20College%20London%20suggested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fpodcasts-for-body-acceptance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebody%20image%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20worsening%20in%20both%20women%20and%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20perhaps%20unsurprising%20that%20body%20dissatisfaction%20has%20increased%2C%20considering%20how%20often%20most%20young%20people%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fhow-social-media-affects-body-image%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20bodies%20tend%20to%20look%20a%20particular%20way%20and%20the%20algorithm%20shows%20more%20of%20the%20same%2C%20Daniels%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20are%20younger%20preteens%20or%20early%20teens%20who%20are%20viewing%20this%20content%2C%20they%20don't%20have%20the%20sophistication%20to%20realize%2C%20%E2%80%98Oh%2C%20this%20guy's%20probably%20making%20this%20up%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20by%20on%20a%20carrot%2C%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20post%20from%20December%202022%20on%20a%20popular%20incel%20forum%2C%20where%20a%20user%20explained%20his%20starvemaxxing%20progress%2C%20lays%20bare%20what%20the%20trend%20could%20be%20doing%20to%20young%20men%E2%80%99s%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20see%20my%20cheekbones%20proper%20but%20maybe%20it%E2%80%99s%20because%20I%20look%20gaunt%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20knees%20%E2%80%9Churt%20like%20shit%E2%80%9D%20when%20he%20walked%2C%20and%20his%20muscles%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cpulsing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20another%20user%20asking%20how%20he%20d