might%20not%20be%20able%20to%3A%20She%20bought%20a%20Corvette%20convertible%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99ve%20bought%20two%20boats%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fishing%20boat%20and%20a%20motor%20yacht.%20They%20recently%20sold%20off%20the%20motor%20yacht%20after%20owning%20it%20for%2012%20years.%20All%20of%20that%20was%20possible%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20children%20and%20have%20been%20strategic%20about%20their%20money%20and%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20live%20the%20boating%20lifestyle%20here%20in%20Virginia.%20We%20went%20and%20did%20that%20every%20weekend%2C%20and%20we%20were%20by%20far%20the%20youngest%20people%20at%20the%20marina%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20something%20that%20we've%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20and%20we%20got%20to%20do%20that%20in%20our%2030s.%20Most%20people%20at%20the%20marina%20were%20already%20retired.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20something%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20take%20for%20granted%3B%20Wasiuk%20said%20she%E2%80%99s%20had%20pinch-me%20moments%20at%20the%20things%20she%E2%80%99s%20been%20able%20to%20do%20and%20is%20consistently%20grateful.%20Her%20parents%20also%20had%20a%20boat%20at%20the%20marina%2C%20and%20they%20were%20able%20to%20join%20Wasiuk%20and%20her%20husband%20for%20boating%20adventures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20couldn't%20ask%20for%20a%20better%20life.%20It%20was%20so%20phenomenal.%20So%20that's%20stuff%20that%20I'll%20always%20have%2C%20and%20we'll%20always%20carry%20with%20us.%20You%20can't%20buy%20that.%20That's%20priceless%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Wasiuk%20received%20a%20few%20stray%20comments%20from%20past%20coworkers%20about%20not%20having%20kids%2C%20she%20said%20it%20happened%20less%20and%20less%20as%20she%20got%20older.%20She%20said%20she%E2%80%99s%20been%20blessed%20with%20a%20supportive%20friend%20network%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20question%20her%20choices.%20Her%20friends%20love%20their%20children%20and%20love%20to%20see%