elhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescue%20operations%20-%20which%20has%20been%20called%20off%20now%20-%20were%20carried%20on%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20fire%20department%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708159080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F46tgk8q_jnu-collapse_625x300_17_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feight-injured-near-delhis-jawaharlal-nehru-stadium-as-temporary-structure-collapses-5074331%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2212%20people%20were%20injured%20when%20a%20temporary%20structure%20near%20Delhi's%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Stadium%20collapses%20today.%20Officials%20are%20trying%20to%20ascertain%20if%20more%20people%20are%20trapped%20under%20the%20debris.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feight-injured-near-delhis-jawaharlal-nehru-stadium-as-temporary-structure-collapses-5074331%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feight-injured-near-delhis-jawaharlal-nehru-stadium-as-temporary-structure-collapses-5074331%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feight-injured-near-delhis-jawaharlal-nehru-stadium-as-temporary-structure-collapses-5074331%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kim%20Ji-woong%20cleared%20of%20alleged%20curse%20controversy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708159059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107775671%2Cimgsize-509093.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fzerobaseones-kim-ji-woong-cleared-of-alleged-curse-controversy-during-fan-video-call-confirms-korea-forensic-science-service%2Farticleshow%2F107775676.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107775676.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFor%20those%20not%20in%20the%20loop%2C%20the%20saga%20began%20on%20February%202%2C%20when%20a%20snippet%20of%20Jiwoong's%20video%20call%20from%20ZEROBASEONE's%20recent%20fansign%20event%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20internet%2C%20alleging%20the%20singer's%20use%20of%20an%20expletive%20after%20bidding%20farewell%20to%20a%20fan.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20brewing%20controversy%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20from%20ZEROBASEONE's%20agency%20pledged%20to%20employ%20digital%20media%20and%20forensic%20techniques%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20situation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Solution%20to%20Farmers'%20Problems%20Lies%20in%20the%20Macro%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16094308%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-9.40.44-AM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20strife%20between%20the%20government%20and%20farm%20unions%20has%20again%20come%20to%20a%20head%20with%20farmers%20heading%20towards%20Delhi%20more%20than%20three%20years%20after%20the%202021%20episode.%20The%20issues%20this%20time%20are%20somewhat%20different%20from%20those%20in%202021-22.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20issue%20was%20the%20repeal%20of%20stealthily%20enacted%20three%20farm%20laws.%20Now%20the%20key%20issue%20is%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20incomes%20via%20a%20legally%20guaranteed%20MSP%20(Minimum%20Support%20Price)%20for%20all%20crops.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELinked%20to%20this%20are%20the%20demand%20for%20debt%20waiver%2C%20pension%2C%20additional%20provision%20for%20MGNREGS%2C%20etc.%20The%20farmers%20have%20also%20widened%20the%20ambit%20of%20their%20protest%20by%20including%20rural%20employment%20and%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20indigenous%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFocus%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20key%20point%20is%20inadequate%20incomes%20of%20a%20vast%20majority%20farmers%20(85%25)%20who%20have%20marginal%20or%20small%20holding%2C%20plowing%20less%20than%202%20hectares%20of%20land.%20Even%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20farmers%20supplement%20their%20income%20from%20agriculture%20through%20other%20work%20or%20business%2C%20like%20agri-businesses.%20Thus%2C%20even%20if%20the%20Punjab%20farmers%20have%20taken%20the%20lead%2C%20they%20represent%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20farming%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20talks%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20farm%20leaders%20having%20failed%2C%20the%20farmers%20decided%20to%20march%20to%20Delhi.%20Trust%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20farmers%20is%20almost%20non-existent%20since%20the%20promises%20made%20in%202022%20when%20the%20farmers%20lifted%20their%20siege%20of%20the%20Capital%20have%20not%20been%20kept.%20The%20doubling%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20incomes%20by%202022%20is%20also%20nowhere%20in%20sight.%20A%20Committee%2C%20set%20up%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20MSP%20and%20reforms%20in%20agriculture%20became%20suspect%20since%20it%20was%20packed%20with%20pro-government%20members%20and%20therefore%20boycotted%20by%20the%20farm%20unions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGovernment%E2%80%99s%20arguments%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20is%20the%20government%20against%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20principal%20demand%20%E2%80%93%20MSP%20for%20all%20crops%20based%20on%20full%20cost%3F%20The%20farmers%20feel%20this%20is%20the%20only%20way%20they%20can%20turn%20the%20currently%20loss%20making%20proposition%20into%20a%20profitable%20one.%20Then%20the%20other%20demands%2C%20like%2C%20debt%20waiver%20would%20lose%20their%20urgency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20the%20arguments%20advanced%20against%20this%20proposition%20are%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a)%20it%20will%20be%20hugely%20expensive%2C%20costing%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20crore.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20cost%20was%20put%20at%20Rs.%2027%20lakh%20crore%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eb)%20The%20entire%20crop%20would%20have%20to%20be%20procured%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Ec)%20This%20would%20not%20be%20administratively%20feasible%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Ed)%20Private%20traders%20would%20stop%20buying%20and%20the%20farmers%20would%20lose%20out%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20e)%20Currently%2C%20only%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20are%20being%20procured%20so%20how%20can%20MSP%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20case%20of%20other%20crops%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20f)%20Only%20the%20big%20farmers%20get%20the%20MSP%3B%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eg)%20Difficulties%20will%20mount%20in%20WTO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FiIwcv7walvY%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22'MSP%20Applies%20to%20Only%2010%25%20of%20Agri%20Households%3B%20Hike%20Farmers%20Want%20Will%20Raise%20Food%20Inflation%20By%2025-30%25'%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20facts%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMSP%20is%20applicable%20to%2023%20crops%20and%20implemented%20only%20for%20wheat%20and%20paddy.%20There%20is%20also%20an%20assured%20price%20for%20sugarcane%20to%20be%20paid%20by%20the%20sugar%20mills.%20So%2C%20these%20three%20crops%20assure%20a%20profit%20which%20other%20crops%20do%20not.%20Hence%20cropping%20pattern%20has%20shifted%20in%20favour%20of%20these%20three%20crops.%20Consequently%2C%20crops%20that%20suit%20a%20agro-climatic%20zone%20are%20not%20grown%20there%20resulting%20in%20environmental%20damage.%20Like%2C%20cultivating%20sugarcane%20in%20water%20starved%20areas%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20paddy%20in%20Punjab.%20The%20result%20is%20excess%20production%20of%20these%20three%20crops%2C%20large%20stocks%20with%20the%20government%20and%20much%20wastage%20since%20there%20is%20inadequate%20storage%20capacity.%20The%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(FCI)%20has%20been%20heavily%20subsidized%20for%20procuring%20and%20holding%20the%20stock%20and%20releasing%20it%20in%20the%20Public%20Distribution%20System%20(PDS).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20MSP%20is%20implemented%20for%20all%20crops%2C%20profitability%20would%20be%20the%20same%20across%20all%20of%20them%20and%20crops%20would%20be%20grown%20based%20on%20their%20suitability%20in%20a%20given%20agro-climatic%20zone.%20That%20would%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a)%20Eliminate%20excess%20stocks%20of%20some%20crops%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eb)%20Reduce%20need%20for%20large%20storage%20capacity%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20c)%20Increase%20production%20of%20those%20crops%2C%20which%20currently%20are%20in%20short%20supply%2C%20like%2C%20oilseeds%3B%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Ed)%20Reduce%20if%20not%20end%20import%20of%20these%20crops%20resulting%20in%20saving%20of%20foreign%20exchange.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20storage%20space%20released%20would%20become%20available%20for%20other%20crops.%20The%20subsidy%20to%20FCI%20would%20drastically%20decline%20and%20food%20wastage%20would%20be%20reduced.%20As%20crops%20suited%20to%20the%20agro-climatic%20conditions%20would%20be%20grown%2C%20environmental%20damage%20would%20decline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20argument%20that%20the%20entire%20crop%20would%20have%20to%20be%20procured%20to%20implement%20MSP%20is%20fallacious.%20Procurement%20would%20be%20required%20only%20when%20the%20price%20drops%20below%20MSP%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20at%20the%20margin.%20As%20excess%20production%20declines%2C%20the%20price%20of%20the%20crops%20would%20rise%20above%20the%20MSP.%20If%20the%20government%20were%20to%20procure%20the%20entire%20crop%20and%20store%20it%20there%20would%20be%20mass%20starvation%20and%20sky%20high%20prices.%20Whatever%20the%20government%20procures%20would%20get%20sold%20in%20the%20market%2C%20so%20it%20would%20only%20need%20working%20capital%20which%20would%20be%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20Rs.10%20lakh%20crore%20bandied%20about.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20would%20be%20a%20win-win%20situation.%20So%2C%20why%20is%20the%20government%20reluctant%20to%20implement%20the%20scheme%3F%20It%20wants%20food%20prices%20to%20remain%20low%20so%20that%20workers%20can%20be%20paid%20a%20low%20wage%20which%20would%20lead%20to%20higher%20profit%20for%20businesses%20and%20benefit%20the%20elite%20which%20needs%20cheap%20labour%20(servants%2C%20drivers%2C%20etc.)%20to%20maintain%20its%20comfortable%20life%20style.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1-1024x768.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697315%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFarmers%20protesting%20in%20Rajpura%20railway%20station%20in%20Punjab.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20Arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EReform%20needed%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20do%20farm%20produce%20prices%20drop%20below%20the%20MSP%3F%20Price%20of%20agricultural%20produce%20is%20demand%20and%20supply%20determined%20because%20there%20are%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20producers%20and%20any%20mismatch%20between%20them%20leads%20to%20price%20changes.%20For%20instance%2C%20supply%20floods%20in%20during%20the%20post-harvest%20period%20ad%20prices%20drop.%20Further%2C%20NHFS%20data%20shows%20that%2030%25%20women%20and%20children%20are%20malnourished.%20They%20are%20not%20able%20to%20afford%20proper%20nutrition%20in%20spite%20of%20government%20providing%20almost%20free%20food%20to%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20implication%20is%20that%20overall%20demand%20is%20low%20due%20to%20large%20scale%20poverty%20and%20that%20is%20why%2C%20farmers%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20remunerative%20price.%20An%20OECD%20study%20estimates%20that%20the%20loss%20to%20Indian%20farmers%20in%202022%20due%20to%20lower%20price%20was%20Rs%2014%20lakh%20crore.%20This%20is%203.5%20times%20the%20subsidy%20to%20farmers.%20That%20is%20why%20MSP%2C%20procurement%20and%20public%20distribution%20become%20crucial.%20If%20workers%20and%20farmers%20had%20a%20civilised%20existence%2C%20these%20would%20not%20be%20needed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20constitution%20promises%20a%20%E2%80%98living%20wage%E2%80%99%20to%20all.%20If%20that%20is%20ensured%2C%20demand%20for%20farm%20produce%20would%20rise%20both%20from%20workers%20and%20farmers%20and%20that%20would%20drive%20prices%20of%20agricultural%20produce%20above%20the%20MSP.%20So%2C%20workers%20are%20the%20natural%20allies%20of%20the%20farmers%20and%20the%20farmers%20ought%20to%20demand%20and%20pay%20them%20a%20%E2%80%98living%20wage%E2%80%99.%20The%20farmers%20would%20not%20lose%20even%20after%20paying%20a%20higher%20wage%20since%20their%20MSP%20would%20be%20determined%20accordingly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHigher%20wages%20and%20prices%20would%20lead%20to%20higher%20inflation%20which%20could%20be%20tackled%20by%20reducing%20indirect%20taxes%20and%20raising%20direct%20taxes.%20In%20the%20alternative%20scenario%20presented%20above%2C%20farm%20subsidies%20would%20decline%20and%20that%20would%20help%20in%20WTO%20negotiations.%20Subsidies%20can%20be%20shifted%20to%20education%2C%20health%2C%20public%20distribution%20system%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20etc.%2C%20so%20that%20neither%20the%20%E2%80%98living%20wage%E2%80%99%20nor%20the%20MSP%20need%20rise%20unduly.%20The%20result%20of%20all%20this%20would%20be%20a%20virtuous%20cycle%20of%20increase%20in%20employment%20and%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findias-wto-stance-on-farmers-will-be-a-test-of-its-rhetoric-of-championing-the-global-south%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20WTO%20Stance%20on%20Farmers%20Will%20Be%20a%20Test%20of%20Its%20Rhetoric%20of%20Championing%20the%20Global%20South%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsidies%20are%20said%20to%20be%20undesirable.%20That%20is%20not%20the%20case%20for%20education%20and%20health%20which%20are%20cases%20of%20merit%20wants%20or%20in%20case%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20like%2C%20communication%20and%20transportation.%20The%20government%20gives%20subsidies%20to%20industry%20and%20calls%20them%20incentives.%20Take%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20which%20offers%20heavy%20subsidies%20to%20big%20corporations%20who%20really%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20them.%20These%20are%20called%20%E2%80%98tax%20expenditures%E2%80%99%20which%20in%202021%20amounted%20to%20Rs%204.48%20lakh%20crores.%20Subsidies%20are%20offered%20on%20land%2C%20water%20and%20electricity%20to%20businesses.%20So%2C%20why%20the%20partiality%20towards%20the%20already%20well%20off%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20argued%20that%20farmers%20should%20take%20up%20employment%20in%20non-agriculture.%20But%2C%20employment%20is%20hardly%20available%20in%20organised%20non-agriculture%20due%20to%20mechanisation%2C%20automation%20and%20now%20use%20of%20AI.%20The%20per%20worker%20output%20in%20the%20organised%20sector%20is%2019%20times%20that%20in%20the%20unorganised%20sector.%20So%2C%20as%20the%20former%20expands%20due%20to%20concessions%20given%20to%20it%2C%20overall%20employment%20contracts.%20Workers%20have%20to%20resort%20to%20self-employment%20at%20low%20wages%20or%20remain%20disguised%20unemployed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20objections%20raised%20against%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands%20are%20only%20scare%20crows%20to%20frighten%20the%20public.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20solution%20to%20farmers%E2%80%99%20problems%20of%20low%20incomes%20lies%20in%20macro%2C%20due%20to%20the%20linkages%20between%20output%2C%20income%20distribution%2C%20prices%2C%20employment%20and%20investment.%20This%20will%20provide%20a%20rational%20long%20term%20policy.%20Piecemeal%20and%20ad%20hoc%20policies%20attempted%20till%20now%20have%20resulted%20in%20contradictions%20and%20persisting%20poverty.%20Of%20late%2C%20farmers%20in%20Europe%20have%20also%20been%20blocking%20roads%20and%20highways%20to%20rise%20their%20demands.%20Clearly%2C%20post%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20adequate%20farm%20incomes%20has%20become%20more%20acute%20globally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20big%20policy%20shift%20would%20take%20a%20few%20years%20to%20fully%20get%20implemented.%20Poverty%20and%20inadequate%20demand%20need%20to%20be%20tackled%20by%20policy%20makers%20by%20focusing%20on%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20vast%20majority%20and%20not%20just%20of%20businesses%20and%20the%20well-off.%20The%20issue%20is%20political%2C%20and%20judges%20whether%20the%20life%20style%20of%20the%20latter%20should%20be%20maintained%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20former.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EArun%20Kumar%20is%20retired%20professor%20of%20economics%2C%20JNU.%20He%20is%20the%20author%20of%20I%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Endian%20Economy%E2%80%99s%20Greatest%20Crisis%3A%20The%20Impact%20of%20Coronavirus%20and%20the%20Road%20Ahead%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708158781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16094308%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-9.40.44-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fthe-solution-to-farmers-problems-lies-in-the-macro%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Poverty%20and%20inadequate%20demand%20need%20to%20be%20tackled%20by%20policy%20makers%20by%20focusing%20on%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20vast%20majority%20and%20not%20just%20of%20businesses%20and%20the%20well-off.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fthe-solution-to-farmers-problems-lies-in-the-macro%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Berlin%E2%80%99s%20Indian%20Trio%20Marks%20Sophomore%20Efforts%20of%20Acclaimed%20Emerging%20Filmmakers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708158600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBerlin-collage.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235891601%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Berlin%20Film%20Festival%20has%20just%20three%20Indian%20narrative%20fiction%20features%20in%20the%202024%20lineup%2C%20but%20all%20of%20them%20are%20sophomore%20efforts%20by%20filmmakers%20who%20have%20already%20won%20global%20acclaim%20for%20their%20debuts.%20Raam%20Reddy%20burst%20onto%20the%20international%20scene%20with%20%E2%80%9CThithi%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%9CFuneral%E2%80%9D)%2C%20which%20won%20the%20Golden%20Leopard%20%E2%80%94%20Filmmakers%20of%