s%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP).%20The%20government%20is%20fuelling%20a%20media-linked%20narrative%20to%20confuse%20people%20that%20guaranteeing%20MSP%20would%20add%20to%20the%20fiscal%20cost%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%2C%20how%20during%20the%20year-long%20Kisan%20Andolan%2C%20a%20guaranteed%20MSP%20was%20one%20of%20the%20two%20main%20demands%20made%20by%20protesting%20farmers%20then.%20The%20first%20was%20for%20repealing%20the%20three-agri%20reform%20laws%20and%20the%20second%20was%20to%20provide%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20on%20MSP.%20While%20the%20Modi%20government%20ultimately%20conceded%20to%20the%20first%2C%20it%20never%20committed%20to%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20can%20MSP%20be%20made%20legally%20binding%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Harish%20Damodaran%20explains%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-the-cost-of-guaranteed-msp-7157934%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%C2%A0there%20are%20two%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20MSP%20can%20be%20made%20legally%20binding%20for%20the%20government.%20The%20%3Cem%3Efirst%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20to%20force%20private%20buyers%20to%20pay%20it.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20no%20crop%20can%20be%20purchased%20below%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Feveryday-explainers%2Ffarmers-crops-price-msp-explained-7789563%2F%5C%22%3EMSP%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20would%20also%20act%20as%20the%20floor%20price%20for%20bidding%20in%20mandi%20auctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20suggested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-the-cost-of-guaranteed-msp-7157934%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20already%20a%20precedent%20for%20private%20players%20to%20pay%20for%20MSP%3A%20In%20sugarcane%2C%20mills%20are%20required%20by%20law%20to%20pay%20growers%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cfair%20and%20remunerative%20price%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%20fix%20even%20higher%20state%20advised%20prices%20%E2%80%93%20within%2014%20days%20of%20supply.%20In%20no%20other%20crop%20is%20the%20compulsion%20to%20pay%20the%20government-announced%20MSP%20thrust%20on%20the%20private%20trade%2Findustry%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Esecond%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroute%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20government%20itself%20buying%20the%20entire%20crop%20that%20farmers%20offer%20at%20the%20MSP.%20This%20would%20mean%20an%20added%20fiscal%20cost%20for%20the%20government%20to%20pay%20for%20this%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fauthor%2F310387%2Fdeepanshu-mohan%5C%22%3Eat%20a%20time%20when%20it%20has%20clearly%20prioritised%20capex-based%20expenditure%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20social%20welfare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20farm%20subsidies%2C%20and%20other%20essential%20scheme-based%20expenditure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202019-20%2C%20before%20the%20Andolan%2C%20government%20agencies%20like%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%2C%20National%20Agricultural%20Cooperative%20Marketing%20Federation%20of%20India%20and%20Cotton%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(CCI)%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-the-cost-of-guaranteed-msp-7157934%2F%5C%22%3Eprocured%2077.34%20million%20tonnes%20(mt)%20of%20paddy%20and%2038.99%20mt%20of%20wheat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20worth%20roughly%20Rs%20140%2C834%20crore%20and%20Rs%2075%2C060%20crore%20at%20their%20respective%20MSPs.%20Further%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-the-cost-of-guaranteed-msp-7157934%2F%5C%22%3Ethey%20purchased%20105.23%20lakh%20bales%20of%20cotton%3C%2Fa%3E%20(MSP%20value%20of%20Rs%2028%2C202%20crore%20in%20terms%20of%20raw%20un-ginned%20kapas)%2C%202.1%20mt%20of%20chana%20or%20chickpea%20(Rs%2010%2C238%20crore)%2C%200.7%20mt%20each%20of%20arhar%20or%20pigeon-pea%20(Rs%204%2C176%20crore)%20and%20groundnut%20(Rs%203%2C614%20crore)%2C%200.8%20mt%20of%20rapeseed-mustard%20(Rs%203%2C540%20crore)%20and%200.1%20mt%20of%20moong%20or%20green%20gram%20(Rs%20987%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20put%20facts%20into%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20is%20projecting%20that%20a%20guaranteed%20MSP%20would%20make%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FHartoshSinghBal%2Fstatus%2F1758010357606465754%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ecost%20by%20Rs%2017%20lakh%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20figure%20is%20incorrect%20and%20the%20argument%20remains%20absurd%20for%20any%20logical%20reason.%20The%20actual%20cost%20of%20running%20an%20MSP%20backed%20by%20the%20government%20payout%20as%20part%20of%20a%20targeted%20scheme%20or%20a%20price%20stabilisation%20fund%20may%20not%20be%20more%20than%20Rs%2050%2C000%20crore.%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fcan-india-actually-afford-msp-for-farmers-its-a-question-of-political-will%2F588793%2F%5C%22%3Eexplained%20in%20this%20excellent%20piece%3C%2Fa%3E%20(back%20in%202021)%20how%20the%20Union%20government%20can%20actually%20help%20farmers%20with%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20explained%20through%20this%20chart%20illustrated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-the-cost-of-guaranteed-msp-7157934%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20MSP%20value%20of%20the%20total%20production%20of%20the%2023%20crops%20(for%20which%20MSP%20is%20currently%20provided)%20worked%20out%20to%20around%20Rs%2010.78%20lakh%20crore%20in%202019-20.%20Not%20all%20this%20produce%20is%20marketed.%20Farmers%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-the-cost-of-guaranteed-msp-7157934%2F%5C%22%3Eretain%20part%20of%20it%20for%20self-consumption%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20seed%20for%20the%20next%20season%E2%80%99s%20sowing%2C%20and%20also%20for%20feeding%20their%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20marketed%20surplus%20ratio%20for%20different%20crops%20is%20estimated%20to%20range%20from%20below%2050%25%20for%20ragi%20and%2065-70%25%20for%20bajra%20(pearl-millet)%20and%20jowar%20(sorghum)%20to%2075%25%20for%20wheat%2C%2080%25%20for%20paddy%2C%2085%25%20for%20sugarcane%2C%2090%25%20for%20most%20pulses%2C%20and%2095%25-plus%20for%20cotton%2C%20jute%2C%20soyabean%20and%20sunflower.%20Taking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-the-cost-of-guaranteed-msp-7157934%2F%5C%22%3Ean%20average%20of%2075%25%20would%20yield%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20number%20of%20just%20over%20Rs%208%20lakh%20crore.%20This%20is%20the%20MSP%20value%20of%20production%2C%20calculated%20by%20Damodaran%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-the-cost-of-guaranteed-msp-7157934%2F%5C%22%3Eestimates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20is%20the%20marketable%20surplus-which%20farmers%20actually%20sell%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20not%20as%20if%20the%20government%20is%20required%20to%20pay%20any%20substantial%20additional%20fiscal%20cost%20to%20incur%20this%2C%20given%20it%20is%20already%20procuring%20paddy%2C%20wheat%2C%20cotton%2C%20pulses%2C%20oilseeds%2C%20etc.(from%20the%2023%20crops%20list)%20at%20MSP.%20Moreover%2C%20as%20done%20for%20sugarcane%20(in%20the%20cited%20reference%20above)%2C%20the%20Union%20and%20the%20State%20Governments%20can%20ask%20private%20firms%2Fbuyers%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20MSP%20from%20what%20they%20buy%2Fsource%20directly%20from%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20iterating%20how%20due%20to%20the%20middle-man%20profiteering%20practices%20seen%20in%20the%20retail%20marketing%20of%20crops%2C%20across%20Indian%20cities%2C%20the%20farmers%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20fair%20share%20of%20return%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98high%20price%E2%80%99%20at%20which%20crops%2C%20vegetables%2C%20or%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20produce%20is%20sold%20in%20the%20urban%20market.%20The%20rising%20urban%20consumer%20bias%2C%20and%20a%20higher%20willingness%20to%20pay%20amongst%20upper%20middle-income%20groups%20and%20richer%20classes%20help%20in%20the%20middle-man%20(intermediary)%20profiteering%20of%20farm%20goods%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20farmer%20welfare%2C%20which%20is%20why%20farmers%20in%20rural%20areas%20need%20more%20price-based%20protection%20via%20MSP%20(richer%20farmers%20of%20states%20like%20Haryana%20and%20Punjab%20have%20made%20the%20government%20more%20accountable%20in%20ensuring%20this).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20own%20concern%20on%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20apathy%20towards%20farmer%20interests%20goes%20beyond%20politics%20alone%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fbudget-2023-is-optimistic-but-indifferent-to-past-failures%5C%22%3Eis%20more%20structural%20to%20the%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20misplaced%20budgetary%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fbudget-2023-is-optimistic-but-indifferent-to-past-failures%5C%22%3Ea%20silent%20fiscal%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20government%20has%20been%20experiencing%20for%20some%20time%20now%20(where%20it%20has%20often%20failed%20to%20collect%20the%20revenue%20it%20outlays%20for%20in%20the%20budgetary%20estimates).%20This%20has%20made%20it%20even%20less%20keen%20to%20support%20farmers%20on%20issues%20like%20MSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20lack%20of%20fiscal%20priority%20attributed%20to%20essential%20spending%20on%20programs%20of%20farm-based%20subsidies%20and%20existing%20costs%2C%20budgeted%20in%20the%20Union%20budgets%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20In%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fbudget%2Fnews%2Frecord-10th-anti-farmer-anti-people-budget-in-a-row-says-kisan-union-124020102017_1.html%5C%22%3Eoverall%20allocations%20for%20agriculture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20allied%20activities%2C%20there%20is%20a%20decline%20of%2022.3%25%20compared%20to%20actual%20expenditure%20in%202022-23%20and%20a%206%25%20decline%20vis%20a%20vis%20the%202023-24%20revised%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Sabha%20(AIKS)%20after%20the%20recent%20Interim%20Union%20budget%20criticised%20the%20Modi%20government%20for%20passing%20an%20anti-farmer-centric%20budget%20for%20the%2010%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%20time%20in%20a%20row.%20AIKS%20argued%20how%20there%20has%20been%20no%20allocation%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20long-standing%20demand%20of%20the%20farmers%20for%20ensuring%20Minimum%20Support%20Prices%20as%20per%20the%20C2%2B50%25%20estimates%20becomes%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fbudget%2Fnews%2Frecord-10th-anti-farmer-anti-people-budget-in-a-row-says-kisan-union-124020102017_1.html%5C%22%3Eallocation%20for%20fertiliser%20subsidy%20in%202024-25%20is%20Rs%2087%2C339%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20less%20than%20the%20actual%20expenditure%20in%202022-23.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fbudget%2Fnews%2Frecord-10th-anti-farmer-anti-people-budget-in-a-row-says-kisan-union-124020102017_1.html%5C%22%3Eallocation%20for%20food%20subsidy%20is%20Rs%206%2C%207552%20crore%20less%20than%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20actual%20expenditure%20in%202022-23.%20This%20was%20accompanied%20by%20budgetary%20cuts%20in%20rural%20development%20schemes%2C%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Krishi%20Sinchai%20Yojana%2C%20cooperation%2C%20food%20storage%20and%20warehousing%2C%20plantations%2C%20crop%20husbandry%2C%20flood%20control%20and%20drainage%2C%20land%20reforms%2C%20fertilizer%20subsidy%2C%20food%20subsidy%2C%20dairy%20development%2C%20soil%20and%20water%20conservation%2C%20irrigation%2C%20nutrition%2C%20rural%20roads%2C%20housing%2C%20education%20and%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20quite%20clear%20from%20these%20macro-fiscal%20numbers%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20fiscal%20priority%20towards%20farmers%20and%20rural%20India%2C%20how%20the%20Modi%20Government%20is%20promoting%20the%20private%20sector%20in%20its%20fiscal%20policy%20and%20is%20still%20ready%20to%20embrace%20a%20strategy%20that%20promotes%20corporatisation%20of%20farming%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20own%20welfare%20and%20economic%20wellbeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20Professor%20of%20Economics%2C%20Dean%2C%20the%20Office%20of%20Interdisciplinarity%20and%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20He%20is%20a%20Visiting%20Professor%20at%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%20and%20Political%20Science%20and%20has%20Visiting%20positions%20at%20University%20of%20London%2C%20University%20of%20Ottawa%2C%20Stellenbosch%20University%20(to%20name%20a%20few).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708155201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27210340%2FEffect.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fon-msp-modi-government-must-display-maturity-and-give-farmers-their-due%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20discussion%20must%20move%20from%20being%20an%20ego%20tussle%20between%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20farmers%2C%20into%20a%20clear%20fiscal%20priority%20for%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fon-msp-modi-government-must-display-maturity-and-give-farmers-their-due%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anil%20celebrates%201%20year%20of%20%E2%80%98The%20Night%20Manager%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708155184000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107773903%2Cimgsize-51890.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanil-kapoor-celebrates-1-year-of-t