20Supriya%20Sule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20yesterday%20hinted%20at%20fielding%20a%20%26quot%3Bfirst-timer%26quot%3B%20from%20Baramati%20against%20Supriya%20Sule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaramati%20has%20traditionally%20been%20a%20bastion%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Supriya%20Sule.%20Ms%20Sule%20has%20represented%20the%20Baramati%20constituency%20for%20three%20consecutive%20terms%20since%202009%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESounding%20the%20election%20bugle%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20said%20that%20he%20would%20field%20a%20candidate%20who%20has%20not%20contested%20an%20election%20earlier%2C%20but%20that%20person%20would%20have%20the%20support%20of%20%26quot%3Bexperienced%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%20made%20an%20emotional%20appeal%20to%20elect%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20timer%26quot%3B%20candidate%20and%20vote%20for%20development%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20come%20to%20you%20and%20ask%20for%20your%20votes%20on%20emotional%20issues%20but%20it%20is%20up%20to%20you%20to%20decide%20whether%20you%20will%20vote%20on%20emotional%20grounds%20or%20to%20continue%20development%20work%20and%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20your%20future%20generations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20formation%20of%20Maharashtra%20state%20and%20the%20commencement%20of%20elections%20till%20date%2C%20it%20has%20never%20happened%20in%20Baramati%20that%20the%20deposit%20of%20opposition%20candidate%20was%20not%20forfeited.%20And%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnReacting%20to%20the%20developments%2C%20Ms%20Sule%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20a%20democracy%2C%20everyone%20here%20has%20the%20right%20to%20contest%20elections%20and%20hence%20it's%20a%20fair%20thing%20to%20say.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20was%20split%20in%20July%20last%20year%20after%20Ajit%20Pawar%20along%20with%20eight%20other%20MLAs%20joined%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Maharashtra%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20earlier%20this%20month%20ruled%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20would%20be%20recognised%20as%20the%20'real%20NCP'%2C%20thereby%20giving%20it%20control%20over%20the%20party%20name%20and%20symbol%20(a%20clock)%20weeks%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20polls%20to%20fill%20six%20to-be-vacant%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20played%20out%20like%20the%20Sena%20Vs%20Sena%20fight%2C%20in%20which%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20(made%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20rebelling%20and%20allying%20with%20the%20BJP)%20was%20called%20the%20'real%20Sena'%2C%20leaving%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20racing%2C%20weeks%20before%20an%20election%2C%20to%20find%20a%20new%20identity%20for%20the%20party%20his%20father%20founded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708154940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fv138fs0o_ajit-pawar-supriya-sule-ani_625x300_17_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbuzz-over-ajit-pawars-wife-vs-supriya-sule-in-family-stronghold-5074145%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pawar%20family%20in%20Maharashtra%20might%20be%20in%20a%20head-to-head%20contest%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%20speculation%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20wife%20Sunetra's%20potential%20candidacy%20against%20his%20cousin%20Supriya%20Sule.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbuzz-over-ajit-pawars-wife-vs-supriya-sule-in-family-stronghold-5074145%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbuzz-over-ajit-pawars-wife-vs-supriya-sule-in-family-stronghold-5074145%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbuzz-over-ajit-pawars-wife-vs-supriya-sule-in-family-stronghold-5074145%2Famp%2F1%2