adlines%20regarding%20the%20veteran%20spinner%20on%20Friday.%20During%20Day%202%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20match%20against%20England%2C%20Ashwin%20received%20a%20five-run%20penalty%20for%20running%20over%20the%C2%A0over%20the%20protected%20area%20of%20the%20pitch.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20England%20started%20their%20first%20innings%20on%205%20for%20no%20loss.%20After%20the%20end%20of%20day's%20play%2C%20Ashwin%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20incident%20and%20took%20complete%20blame%20for%20the%20five-run%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BMy%20poor%20motor%20skills%20didn't%20allow%20me%20to%20get%20off%20the%20pitch%20in%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20in%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ICC%20law%2C%20the%20protected%20area%20of%20the%20pitch%20is%20%26quot%3Bthat%20area%20of%20the%20pitch%20contained%20within%20a%20rectangle%20bounded%20at%20each%20end%20by%20imaginary%20lines%20parallel%20to%20the%20popping%20creases%20and%205%20ft%2F1.52%20m%20in%20front%20of%20each%2C%20and%20on%20the%20sides%20by%20imaginary%20lines%2C%20one%20each%20side%20of%20the%20imaginary%20line%20joining%20the%20centres%20of%20the%20two%20middle%20stumps%2C%20each%20parallel%20to%20it%20and%201%20ft%2F30.48%20cm%20from%20it%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ben%20Duckett%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63527-ben-matthew-duckett-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBen%20Duckett%3C%2Fa%3E%20smashed%20a%20century%20to%20lead%20England's%20attacking%20reply%20of%20207-2%20on%20Friday%20after%20Indian%20spinner%20Ravichandran%C2%A0Ashwin%C2%A0reached%20500%20Test%20wickets%20in%20the%20third%20match%20of%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-handed%20Duckett%20reached%20his%20third%20Test%20hundred%20in%2088%20balls%20as%20England%20reached%20207-2%20to%20cut%20their%20deficit%20after%20they%20bowled%20out%20India%20for%20445%20on%20day%20two%20in%20Rajkot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3