stody.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Country%20Is%20Best%20For%20Indians%20To%20Build%20Multi-Generational%20Wealth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESwitzerland%20is%20the%20world's%20best%20nation%20to%20build%20multi-generational%20wealth.%20As%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.henleyglobal.com%2Fpublications%2Fhenley-education-report%5C%22%3Enew%20index%20by%20citizenship%20advisory%20firm%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Switzerland%20has%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20opportunity%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20index%20evaluated%20the%20nations%20on%20six%20different%20parameters%20including%20earning%20potential%2C%20career%20advancement%2C%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20premium%20education%2C%20economic%20mobility%2C%20and%20livability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWith%20100%20points%20of%20earning%20potential%2C%2095%20points%20of%20career%20advancement%2C%20and%2094%20points%20of%20employment%20prospects%2C%20Switzerland%20has%20occupied%20the%20top%20spot%20on%20the%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20high%20livability%20and%20economic%20mobility%2C%20Switzerland%20scored%2075%20points%2C%20while%20it%20scored%2072%20on%20premium%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESwitzerland%20is%20followed%20by%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20which%20scored%2082%20per%20cent%20on%20the%20total%20opportunity%20score.%20The%20US%20stands%20equivalent%20to%20Switzerland%20on%20employment%20prospects%E2%80%9494%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20it%20dwindled%20to%2093%20points%20on%20earning%20potential%2C%2086%20points%20on%20career%20advancement%2C%20and%2068%20points%20on%20high%20livability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20employment%20prospects%20and%20premium%20education%20in%20the%20USA%20stand%20at%2074%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndia%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20scored%2032%20per%20cent%20on%20the%20opportunity%20score%2C%20which%20is%20even%20lower%20than%20Greece%20and%20occupies%20the%20last%20spot%20among%20the%20top%2015%20nations%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndia%20has%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20scores%20on%20economic%20mobility%2C%20which%20is%20just%208%20points.%20Among%20its%20other%20parameters%2C%20India%20has%20the%20highest%20career%20advancement%20with%2043%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDespite%20scoring%20a%20similar%20earning%20potential%20that%20of%20Switzerland%20(100%20points)%2C%20Singapore%20occupied%20third%20place%20on%20the%20Index%20as%20it%20got%20a%2079%20per%20cent%20total%20opportunity%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAfter%20scoring%2097%20points%2C%20Singapore%20has%20garnered%20the%20highest%20employment%20prospect%20score%20on%20the%20list%2C%20which%20includes%2015%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESingapore%20has%20the%20least%20career%20advancement%20among%20the%20top%205%20nations%20on%20the%20index.%20Apart%20from%2066%20points%20in%20career%20advancement%2C%20the%20nation%20has%20scored%2055%20points%20in%20premium%20education%2C%2065%20points%20in%20high%20livability%20and%2092%20in%20economic%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAustralia%20was%20at%20the%20fourth%20place%20with%20a%2075%20per%20cent%20total%20opportunity%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20island%20nation%20has%20amassed%2066%20points%20on%20earning%20potential%2C%2079%20on%20career%20advancement%2C%2084%20on%20employment%20prospects%2C%2073%20on%20premium%20education%20and%2074%20both%20on%20economic%20mobility%20and%20high%20livability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20top%205%20places%20ended%20with%20Canada%20standing%20in%20fifth%20position%20after%20it%20received%20a%2074%20per%20cent%20total%20opportunity%20score.%20Canada's%20employment%20prospects%20stood%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20Australia's%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20North%20American%20nation%20amassed%2067%20points%20on%20earning%20potential%2C%2079%20on%20career%20advancement%2C%2071%20on%20premium%20education%2C%2073%20on%20economic%20mobility%20and%2072%20on%20high%20livability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWith%2049%20per%20cent%20on%20the%20total%20opportunity%20score%2C%20Greece%20stands%20last%20in%20the%20index%20of%2015%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708143840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fbvi4ug4_switzerland_625x300_04_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fswitzerland-is-best-country-to-build-multi-generational-wealth-5070302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Switzerland%20is%20the%20world's%20best%20nation%20to%20build%20multi-generational%20wealth.%20As%20per%20a%20new%20index%20by%20citizenship%20advisory%20firm%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%2C%20Switzerland%20has%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20opportunity%20score.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fswitzerland-is-best-country-to-build-multi-generational-wealth-5070302%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fswitzerland-is-best-country-to-build-multi-generational-wealth-5070302%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fswitzerland-is-best-country-to-build-multi-generational-wealth-5070302%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20disables%20web%20apps%20on%20iPhones%20in%20European%20Union%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708143456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2