ow%2F107769479.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judge%20declares%2C%20then%20retracts%2C%20a%20mistrial%20in%20the%20murder%20trial%20of%20a%20former%20Ohio%20deputy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708142094000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107769511%2Cimgsize-594198.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjudge-declares-then-retracts-a-mistrial-in-the-murder-trial-of-a-former-ohio-deputy%2Farticleshow%2F107769391.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107769391.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20murder%20trial%20of%20Jason%20Meade%2C%20who%20shot%20Casey%20Goodson%20Jr.%2C%20a%20mistrial%20declaration%20was%20retracted.%20Goodson%20was%20holding%20a%20sandwich%20bag%20when%20fatally%20shot.%20The%20jury%20was%20unsettled%2C%20and%20alternate%20jurors%20were%20elevated.%20Goodson's%20gun%20was%20found%20with%20the%20safety%20mechanism%20engaged.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjudge-declares-then-retracts-a-mistrial-in-the-murder-trial-of-a-former-ohio-deputy%2Farticleshow%2F107769391.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjudge-declares-then-retracts-a-mistrial-in-the-murder-trial-of-a-former-ohio-deputy%2Famp_articleshow%2F107769391.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjudge-declares-then-retracts-a-mistrial-in-the-murder-trial-of-a-former-ohio-deputy%2Famp_articleshow%2F107769391.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20Doctors%20Shocked%20After%20Man%2C%2073%2C%20Inserts%20Batteries%20Into%20His%20Penis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2073-year-old%20Australian%20man%20sought%20urgent%20medical%20help%20after%20jamming%20three%20button-style%20batteries%20into%20his%20penis.%20According%20to%20the%20medical%20study%20published%20in%20Urology%20Case%20Reports%2C%20the%20unidentified%20man%20had%20been%20fueling%20his%20own%20%26quot%3Bsexual%20gratification%26quot%3B%20by%20intentionally%20shoving%20batteries%20into%20his%20penile%20urethra.%20He%20admitted%20to%20regularly%20inserting%20foreign%20objects%20without%20them%20getting%20stuck%20inside..%20However%2C%20this%20time%2C%20the%20batteries%20had%20moved%20further%20up%20the%20penile%20urethra%20due%20to%20repeated%20failed%20attempts%20at%20self-removal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20best%20of%20our%20understanding%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20reported%20case%20of%20urethral%20necrosis%20with%20button%20battery%20insertion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS221444202400007X%3Fdgcid%3Draven_sd_aip_email%5C%22%3Estudy%20%3C%2Fa%3Eauthors%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20seeked%20medical%20attention%2024%20hours%20after%20inserting%20three%20button%20batteries%20into%20his%20penile%20urethra.%20He%20presented%20to%20the%20emergency%20department%20with%20moderate%20penile%20pain%2C%20severe%20paraphimosis%20and%20obstructive%20urinary%20symptoms%20including%20weak%20urinary%20flow%2C%20straining%20and%20a%20sensation%20of%20incomplete%20bladder%20emptying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20then%20moved%20quickly%20to%20remove%20the%20foreign%20objects%20as%20their%20corrosiveness%20can%20cause%20necrosis%20-%20the%20death%20of%20body%20tissue%20-%20in%20just%20two%20hours.%20The%20doctors%20also%20feared%20the%20potentially%20rare%20but%20lethal%20infection%20of%20Fournier's%20gangrene%20-%20a%20type%20of%20flesh-eating%20disease%20that%20affects%20your%20scrotum%2C%20penis%20or%20perineum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20unsuccessful%20approaches%2C%20the%20doctors%20were%20finally%20able%20to%20remove%20the%20batteries%20using%20forceps.%20%26quot%3BAll%20extracted%20batteries%20were%20coated%20with%20black%20tar-like%20material%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fuk-scientists-develop-new-wonder-drug-that-offers-breakthrough-treatment-of-deadly-cancer-5067183%5C%22%3EUK%20Scientists%20Develop%20New%20%26quot%3BWonder%26quot%3B%20Drug%20That%20Offers%20Breakthrough%20Treatment%20Of%20Deadly%20Cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20wasn't%20the%20end%20as%20the%20man%20returned%20to%20the%20hospital%2010%20days%20later%2C%20complaining%20of%20swelling%20and%20icky%20discharge.%20The%20doctors%20then%20quickly%20operated%20on%20him%20again.%20%26quot%3BAn%20incision%20was%20made%20to%20the%20penile%20skin%2C%26quot%3B%20researchers%20noted%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20large%20amount%26quot%3B%20of%20fluids%20leaked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20study%2C%20the%20doctors'%20fears%20that%20the%20man%20developed%20an%20%26quot%3Bextensive%20degree%20of%20necrosis%26quot%3B%20were%20realised.%20Part%20of%20the%20man's%20urethra%20had%20to%20be%20removed%2C%20the%20study%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20complexity%20of%20his%20injury%2C%20it%20was%20deemed%20that%20formal%20penile%20urethral%20reconstruction%20would%20likely%20require%20a%203-stage%20repair%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20researchers%2C%20who%20described%20the%20complex%2C%20six-month%20procedure%20of%20mucous%20membrane%20grafts.%20After%20assessing%20the%20extremely%20damaged%20penis%2C%20ultimately%20doctors%20%26quot%3Bdecided%20that%20the%20best%20option%20would%20be%20for%20no%20further%20penile%20reconstruction%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708141980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fe5i30qh8_doctor-generic_625x300_17_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%2