0years%20old%2C%20fills%20him%20with%20regret.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDacoits%20led%20by%20bandit%20leader%20Phoolan%20Devi%20%E2%80%93%20who%20later%20went%20on%20to%20gain%20iconic%20status%20as%20a%20backward%20caste%20bandit-turned-parliamentarian%20%E2%80%93%20dressed%20in%20police%20fatigues%20had%20entered%20the%20village%20from%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Yamuna%20River%2C%20which%20cradles%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20dacoits%2C%20or%20%3Cem%3Ebaaghis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(rebels)%20as%20they%20liked%20to%20be%20called%2C%20rounded%20up%20all%20the%20men%20and%20held%20them%20at%20gunpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBabuji%E2%80%99s%20father%20Himmat%20Singh%20was%20holding%20him%2C%20a%20child%20barely%20five%20years%20old%2C%20when%20the%20dacoits%20asked%20him%20how%20many%20children%20he%20had.%20When%20Himmat%20Singh%20told%20them%20that%20Babuji%20was%20his%20only%20son%2C%20they%20told%20him%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20boy.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20spared%20me%20because%20I%20was%20his%20only%20son.%20My%20father%20dropped%20me%20and%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20remember%20is%20that%20he%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98Son%20you%20go%20home%2C%20I%20will%20not%20be%20coming%20back%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Babuji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133210%2FPSX_20240215_184122.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133210%2FPSX_20240215_184122.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133210%2FPSX_20240215_184122-300x180.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133210%2FPSX_20240215_184122-1024x613.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697467%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBabuji%20Singh%20(Right).%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHimmat%20Singh%20and%20Babuji%E2%80%99s%20two%20cousins%20were%20among%20the%2020%20villagers%20who%20were%20executed%20by%20Phoolan%20Devi%20and%20her%20gang%20of%20bandits%20in%20Behmai%20village%2C%20which%20is%20today%20located%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kanpur%20Dehat%20district.%20His%20father%E2%80%99s%20death%20sprung%20back%20into%20Babuji%E2%80%99s%20consciousness%20not%20only%20because%20February%2014%2C%202024%20%E2%80%93%20Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20to%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20was%20the%2043rd%20anniversary%20of%20his%20loss%2C%20but%20also%20the%20day%20when%20a%20court%20in%20Kanpur%20Dehat%20finally%20pronounced%20the%20verdict%20in%20the%20Behmai%20massacre%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20special%20judge%20(dacoity%20affected%20areas)%20convicted%20one%20of%20the%20five%20accused%20who%20were%20chargesheeted%20in%20the%20case.%20Shyam%20Babu%20Kewat%2C%20the%20convicted%20member%20of%20Phoolan%20Devi%E2%80%99s%20gang%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20under%20the%20charge%20of%20murder%20during%20dacoity%20(Section%20396%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%2035-36%20dacoits%20from%20four%20different%20gangs%20had%20been%20booked%20for%20the%20crime%20in%201981%2C%20eventually%2C%20only%20five%20faced%20trial%20and%20only%20two%20survived%20to%20see%20the%20verdict.%20While%20Shyam%20Babu%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Auraiya%2C%20was%20convicted%2C%20another%20accused%20Vishwanath%20alias%20Putani%20was%20acquitted%20as%20he%20got%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbenefit%20of%20doubt%E2%80%9D%20for%20being%20a%20minor%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20crime%2C%20said%20Raju%20Porwal%2C%20district%20government%20counsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202015%2C%20a%20local%20court%20ruled%20that%20Vishwanath%20was%20indeed%20a%20minor%20%E2%80%93%2015%20years%2C%20seven%20months%20and%2013%20days%20old%2C%20to%20be%20precise%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20massacre%20and%20declared%20him%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdelinquent%20juvenile.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20popular%20narrative%20is%20that%20Phoolan%20stormed%20the%20village%20in%20search%20of%20two%20Thakur%20gang%20leaders%20who%20had%20raped%20and%20brutalized%20her%20and%20also%20shot%20dead%20her%20paramour.%20She%20wanted%20to%20punish%20the%20villagers%20for%20providing%20them%20shelter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELocal%20Thakurs%2C%20however%2C%20contested%20this%20version%20and%20said%20that%20they%20paid%20a%20price%20for%20getting%20caught%20in%20the%20war%20between%20backward%20caste%20and%20Thakur%20dacoit%20gangs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBabuji%20said%20the%20delayed%20verdict%20%E2%80%93%20after%20an%20excruciatingly%20long%20wait%20of%20more%20than%20four%20decades%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20conviction%20of%20just%20one%20of%20the%20dozens%20of%20accused%2C%20was%20a%20mockery%20of%20justice.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20get%20justice.%20They%20have%20played%20with%20us.%20What%20use%20is%20convicting%20one%20person%20and%20sentencing%20him%20for%20life%20after%2043%20years%3F%20What%E2%80%99s%20left%20in%20it%20for%20us%20now%3F%20Even%20my%20mother%20is%20dead%2C%E2%80%9D%20Babuji%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20feels%20the%20only%20way%20he%20and%20other%20surviving%20kin%20of%20those%20murdered%20in%20Behmai%20would%20get%20solace%20was%20if%20the%20accused%20received%20a%20death%20penalty.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20should%20be%20hanged.%20Only%20then%20will%20our%20%3Cem%3Eatmas%3C%2Fem%3E%20get%20shanti%2C%E2%80%9D%20Babuji%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBehmai%20is%20nestled%20in%20the%20ravines%20of%20the%20Yamuna%20valley%20near%20Chambal.%20In%20the%20decades%20where%20dacoits%20ruled%20the%20ravines%2C%20the%20village%2C%20due%20to%20its%20undulated%20topography%2C%20dense%20overgrowth%20and%20access%20to%20the%20river%20for%20escape%2C%20served%20as%20a%20getaway%20and%20safe%20haven%20for%20dacoits.%20Today%2C%20the%20ravines%20have%20been%20cropped%20to%20accommodate%20%3Cem%3Epucca%3C%2Fem%3E%20roads%20but%20the%20village%20still%20struggles%20without%20basic%20amenities.%20Most%20of%20the%20men%20serve%20as%20migrant%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133707%2FPSX_20240215_183915.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133707%2FPSX_20240215_183915.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133707%2FPSX_20240215_183915-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133707%2FPSX_20240215_183915-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697471%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShahid%20Smarak.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20police%20outpost%20and%20a%20memorial%20%E2%80%93%20Shaheed%20Smarak%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20village%20is%20the%20only%20remnant%20of%20the%201981%20incident%20and%20those%20treacherous%20times.%20The%20memorial%20has%20the%20list%20of%20all%2020%20persons%20who%20were%20killed.%20It%20refers%20to%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunarmed%2C%20innocent%20and%20noble%E2%80%9D%20men%20who%20were%20killed%20at%204%20pm%20on%20February%2014%2C%201981.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAll%2020%20who%20were%20killed%20were%20men%2C%20aged%2016-55.%20Seventeen%20of%20them%20belonged%20to%20the%20Thakur%20community.%20Dalit%20labourers%20from%20Rajapur%20and%20a%20Muslim%20from%20Sikandara%2C%20who%20were%20in%20the%20village%20on%20assignment%2C%20were%20also%20killed.%20Six%20others%2C%20including%20an%20uncle%20of%20Babuji%2C%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20372px)%2085vw%2C%20372px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133415%2FPSX_20240215_183901.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22372%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133415%2FPSX_20240215_183901.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133415%2FPSX_20240215_183901-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133415%2FPSX_20240215_183901-768x1024.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697468%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22496%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENames%20on%20the%20Shahid%20Smarak.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20one%20can%20imagine%2C%20the%20legal%20case%20in%20the%20crime%20moved%20at%20an%20agonizingly%20slow%20pace%2C%20exposing%20the%20slow%20mechanism%20of%20grievance%20redressal%20in%20our%20country%2C%20especially%20in%20smaller%20towns%20away%20from%20daily%20media%20glare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20charges%20against%20the%20five%20surviving%20accused%20Maan%20Singh%2C%20Vishwanath%2C%20Posa%2C%20Ram%20Ratan%20and%20Shyam%20Babu%20were%20framed%20only%20in%20August%202012.%20The%20trial%20started%20five%20years%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20initial%20FIR%20lodged%20at%20Sikandara%20police%20station%2C%20which%20was%20then%20in%20undivided%20Kanpur%2C%20was%20lodged%20against%20four%20dacoits%20including%20Phoolan%20Devi%20and%20bandit%20leader%20Mustaqim%2C%20and%2036%20unnamed%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMaan%20Singh%2C%20Phoolan%E2%80%99s%20close%20aide%2C%20never%20appeared%20before%20the%20court%20despite%20having%20charges%20framed%20against%20him%20and%20being%20summoned.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20prosecution%20had%20even%20submitted%20that%20Maan%20Singh%20was%20running%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Chaura%20but%20never%20appeared%20before%20court.%20Summons%20were%20served%20to%20him%20and%2C%20last%20April%2C%20a%20court%20even%20issued%20a%20non-bailable%20warrant%20against%20him%20and%20gave%20orders%20to%20attach%20two%20of%20his%20identified%20properties.%20But%20it%20is%20suspected%20that%20Singh%20may%20have%20passed%20away%20in%20the%20meantime%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMost%20of%20the%20other%20accused%20either%20died%20or%20were%20shot%20dead%20by%20police%20or%20rivals%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPhoolan%20had%20surrendered%20to%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20police.%20After%20spending%2011%20years%20in%20jails%20in%20MP%2C%20she%20was%20released%20in%201994%20after%20the%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20government%20in%20UP%20withdrew%20the%20cases%20against%20her.%20Phoolan%2C%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20Nishad%20OBC%20riverine%20community%2C%20then%20went%20on%20to%20win%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Mirzapur%20in%20Purvanchal%20in%201996%20and%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20local%20court%2C%20however%2C%20set%20aside%20the%20Mulayam%20Singh%20government%20decision.%20This%20was%20upheld%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20But%20before%20Phoolan%20Devi%20could%20surrender%20before%20the%20trial%20court%20to%20avail%20any%20sort%20of%20relief%2C%20she%20was%20murdered%20outside%20her%20official%20residence%20in%202001.%20A%20Thakur%20man%20Sher%20Singh%20Rana%2C%20who%20despised%20her%20for%20murdering%20Thakur%20men%2C%20was%20later%20convicted%20for%20her%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20widely%20believed%20that%20Phoolan%20allegedly%20committed%20the%20Behmai%20massacre%20to%20avenge%20her%20rape%20and%20humiliation%20in%20the%20village%20by%20Lala%20Ram%20and%20Sri%20Ram%2C%20two%20Thakur%20gang%20leaders%20and%20her%20rivals%20who%20had%20also%20shot%20dead%20her%20alleged%20paramour%20Vikram%20Mallah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20two%20brothers%2C%20like%20other%20dacoits%2C%20would%20often%20frequent%20Behmai%2C%20which%20was%20dominated%20by%20their%20caste%20fellows.%20Shekhar%20Kapur%E2%80%99s%20well-known%20movie%20%3Cem%3EBandit%20Queen%20(1994)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20traces%20Phoolan%E2%80%99s%20journey%2C%20plays%20out%20this%20sequence%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20fictionalised%20manner.%20She%20had%20herself%20refuted%20the%20narrative%20and%20some%20of%20the%20events%20shown%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20and%20even%20approached%20court%20seeking%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20showcasing%20of%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELocals%20in%20Behmai%20refute%20the%20revenge%20for%20rape%20theory.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20can%20rape%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebadmaash%3C%2Fem%3E%20(dacoit)%3F%20One%20with%20guns%20and%20a%20gang!%20It%20was%20only%20after%20she%20got%20fame%20through%20the%20film%20Bandit%20Queen%20that%20this%20narrative%20spread%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Babuji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20insists%20that%20the%20Behmai%20massacre%20took%20place%20as%20Phoolan%20suspected%20that%20the%20local%20Thakurs%20were%20providing%20refuge%20to%20her%20rival%20Thakur%20gangs.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBas%20badmasho%20ka%20vivaad%20tha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(It%20was%20all%20about%20a%20dispute%20between%20the%20dacoits)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20year%20too%2C%20the%20villagers%20of%20Behmai%20gathered%20at%20the%20Shaheed%20Smarak%20at%2011%20am%20on%20February%2014%20to%20remember%20those%20who%20were%20killed%20in%201981.%20A%20second%20gathering%20was%20organized%20for%20later%20in%20the%20day%20in%20hope%20that%20the%20court%20would%20sentence%20the%20accused%20to%20death.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20verdict%20was%20nothing%20great.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20a%20formality%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Babuji.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%2043%20years%2C%20the%20entire%20country%20has%20changed.%20But%20Behmai%20remains%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133651%2FPSX_20240215_183937.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133651%2FPSX_20240215_183937.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133651%2FPSX_20240215_183937-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133651%2FPSX_20240215_183937-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697470%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERajaram%20Singh%2C%20man%20in%20brown%20cardigan%2C%20the%20main%20plaintiff%20amd%20witness%20in%20the%20Behmai%20massacre.%20He%20died%20in%202020.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202020%2C%20Rajaram%20Singh%2C%20an%20eyewitness%20to%20the%20massacre%20and%20one%20who%20led%20the%20legal%20fight%20for%20decades%2C%20had%20shared%20a%20similar%20narrative%20with%20me%20when%20I%20met%20him%20in%20his%20house.%20He%20did%20not%20have%20any%20sympathy%20for%20Phoolan%20and%20claimed%20that%20dacoits%20shot%20the%20villagers%20because%20some%20of%20them%20had%20acted%20as%20informants%20for%20the%20police.%20He%20also%20dismissed%20the%20rape%20theory.%20Rajaram%20lost%20seven%20relatives%2C%20including%20his%20brother%20Banwari%20Singh%20on%20February%2014%2C%201981.%20In%20January%202020%2C%20a%20special%20court%20(dacoity)%20fixed%20a%20date%20for%20pronouncing%20the%20verdict%2C%20igniting%20a%20hope%20for%20justice%20in%20him.%20But%20the%20verdict%20was%20deferred%20on%20grounds%20that%20the%20original%20case%20diary%20was%20curiously%20found%20missing%20in%20the%20court%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERajaram%20was%20returning%20from%20the%20fields%20when%20he%20spotted%20the%20dacoits%20storming%20the%20village.%20To%20save%20his%20life%2C%20he%20hid%20in%20the%20bushes%20and%20witnessed%20the%20bloodshed%20from%20there.%E2%80%9DShe%20%5BPhoolan%5D%20shouted%20%3Cem%3EJai%20Kali%20Mai%20ki%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20badmash%20started%20firing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajaram%20told%20me%20in%20December%202020%2C%20as%20he%20recounted%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERajaram%20died%20later%20in%20the%20same%20month%2C%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20after%20we%20last%20met%2C%20with%20his%20quest%20for%20justice%20unfulfilled.%20In%20October%202021%2C%20Jantar%20Singh%2C%20the%20last%20surviving%20witness%20in%20the%20case%2C%20also%20died%20in%20his%20seventies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFollowing%20that%2C%20Babuji%20took%20over%20as%20the%20plaintiff%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPorwal%20said%20Shyam%20Babu%20was%20convicted%20after%20the%20prosecution%20proved%20in%20court%20the%20%E2%80%9Centire%20circumstances%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20incident.%20The%20conviction%20was%20also%20based%20on%20the%20identification%20parade%20of%20the%20accused%20carried%20out%20in%20different%20jails%20following%20the%20incident%20and%20on%20statements%20of%20the%20surviving%20witnesses%2C%20said%20Porwal.%20A%20detailed%20order%20of%20the%20verdict%20is%20not%20yet%20accessible.%20A%20key%20question%20in%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20mind%20is%20what%20does%20the%20court%20say%20on%20the%20role%20of%20Phoolan%20Devi%20and%20the%20motivation%20behind%20the%20crime%2C%20known%20to%20us%20as%20the%20Behmai%20massacre.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708137022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16133707%2FPSX_20240215_183915.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2F43-years-20-massacred-1-conviction-what-became-of-the-phoolan-devi-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dacoits%20led%20by%20bandit%20leader%20Phoolan%20Devi%20had%20killed%2020%20villagers%20from%20Behmai%20on%20February%2014%2C%201981.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2F43-years-20-massacred-1-conviction-what-became-of-the-phoolan-devi-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Carnival%2C%20kisses%20and%20snow%3A%20Photos%20of%20the%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708136726000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2888%2Fproduction%2F_132667301_gettyimages-1999100804.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fin-pictures-68315599%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20selection%20of%20striking%20images%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20taken%20over%20the%20past%20seven%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fin-pictures-68315599%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fin-pictures-68315599.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fin-pictures-68315599.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20army%20chief%20says%20forces%20have%20pulled%20out%20of%20frontline%20city