22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERep.%20Kera%20Birkeland%2C%20R-Morgan%2C%20of%20the%20Utah%20House%20of%20Representatives%3Cp%3ERick%20Bowmer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUtah%20legislature%20approved%20a%20bill%20on%20NDAs%20related%20to%20sexual%20assault%20and%20harassment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bill%2C%20if%20passed%2C%20would%20make%20confidentiality%20clauses%20from%20January%201%2C%202023%2C%20onwards%20unenforceable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bill%20also%20says%20attempts%20to%20enforce%20a%20confidentiality%20clause%20could%20result%20in%20liability%20for%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Utah%20state%20legislature%20passed%20a%20bill%20on%20Friday%20that%20makes%20confidentiality%20clauses%20related%20to%20sexual%20assault%20and%20sexual%20harassment%20unenforceable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fle.utah.gov%2F~2024%2Fbills%2Fstatic%2FHB0055.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EHB55%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sponsored%20by%20Rep.%20Kera%20Birkeland%2C%20passed%20in%20Utah's%20House%20and%20Senate%20with%20amendments%20this%20week.%20The%20next%20step%20is%20for%20the%20bill%20to%20be%20enrolled%20to%20be%20prepared%20in%20final%20form%20and%20then%20sent%20to%20the%20governor%20to%20sign%2C%20veto%2C%20or%20allow%20it%20to%20become%20law%20without%20his%20signature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20important%20development%20in%20Utah%2C%20a%20state%20where%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-utah-silicon-slopes-difficulties-tech-jobs-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewomen%20have%20reported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20experiencing%20a%20culture%20of%20sexism%20and%20even%20harassment%20at%20companies%20they've%20worked%20at.%20Nationwide%2C%20confidentiality%20clauses%2C%20often%20in%20the%20form%20of%20nondisclosure%20and%20non-disparagement%20agreements%2C%20can%20be%20commonplace%20and%20keep%20employees%20from%20reporting%20cases%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20or%20assault%20at%20their%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Utah's%20House%2C%20the%20bill%20with%20amendments%20from%20the%20Senate%20passed%20Friday%20with%2071%20representatives%20in%20favor%20and%204%20representatives%20absent%20or%20not%20voting.%20In%20the%20state's%20Senate%2C%20it%20passed%20Wednesday%20with%2024%20senators%20in%20favor%20and%205%20senators%20absent%20or%20not%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Utah's%20governor%20signs%20the%20bill%20into%20law%2C%20it%20will%20apply%20to%20confidentiality%20clauses%20in%20Utah%20that%20were%20in%20effect%20from%20January%201%2C%202023%2C%20onward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20woman%20speaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20women%2C%20I%20hope%20it%20brings%20upon%20Utah%20future%20change%20for%20the%20better%20to%20have%20a%20better%20workplace%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kimberly%20Bernhardt%2C%20an%20advocate%20with%20the%20group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usu.edu%2Fuwlp%2Fa-bolder-way-forward%2Foverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EA%20Bolder%20Way%20Forward%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20championed%20the%20bill%20and%20testified%20to%20the%20House%20Judiciary%20Committee%20in%20support%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDAs%20in%20the%20workplace%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAdvocates%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usu.edu%2Fuwlp%2Fa-bolder-way-forward%2Foverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EA%20Bolder%20Way%20Forward%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20gauge%20exactly%20how%20widespread%20these%20types%20of%20confidentiality%20agreements%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNondisclosure%20agreements%20tend%20to%20make%20people%20not%20talk%20about%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernhardt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20happens%20to%20you%20outside%20of%20work%2C%20people%20can%20talk%20about%20it%20all%20they%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BNormal%20citizens%20have%20legal%20remedy%20for%20defamation%20if%20it%20hurts%20their%20reputation%20outside%20of%20employment.%20Within%20employment%2C%20there's%20just%20a%20different%20set%20of%20laws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20about%2011%25%20of%20respondents%20agreed%20or%20strongly%20agreed%20that%20most%20organizations%20in%20Utah%20%26quot%3Bwould%20appropriately%20handle%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usu.edu%2Fuwlp%2Ffiles%2Fsexual-harassment-gender-based-discrimination-research-summary.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20statewide%20study%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20by%20the%20Utah%20Women%20%26amp%3B%20Leadership%20Project.%20And%20nationwide%2C%20more%20than%202%20out%20of%203%20sexual%20assaults%20go%20unreported%20to%20the%20police%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rainn.org%2Fstatistics%2Fcriminal-justice-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20RAINN%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Congress%20passed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F117th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F4524%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESpeak%20Now%20Act%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20which%20prohibits%20the%20enforceability%20of%20a%20nondisclosure%20or%20nondisparagement%20clause%20agreed%20to%20before%20a%20dispute%20that%20arises%20involving%20sexual%20assault%20or%20harassment.%20But%20this%20federal%20law%20doesn't%20apply%20to%20NDAs%20signed%20as%20a%20result%20of%20such%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20high%20cost%20of%20legal%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Utah%20bill%20also%20states%20that%20someone%20who%20attempts%20to%20enforce%20a%20confidentiality%20clause%20may%20be%20liable%20for%20costs%20and%20attorney%20fees%20under%20certain%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20bill%2C%20an%20employer%20that%20tries%20to%20enforce%20a%20confidentiality%20clause%20would%20be%20liable%20for%20all%20costs%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20attorney%20fees%2C%26quot%3B%20resulting%20from%20legal%20action%20to%20enforce%20the%20clause%20and%20is%20not%20entitled%20to%20monetary%20damages%20for%20breaching%20that%20clause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20most%20sexual%20harassment%20cases%2C%20a%20company%20is%20fully%20equipped%20with%20lawyers%20at%20their%20beck%20and%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernhardt%20said.%20%26quot%3BRegular%20people%20and%20employees%20don't%20just%20have%20a%20lawyer%20they%20can%20dial%20for%20help.%20When%20individuals%20report%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20don't%20have%20attorneys.%20If%20a%20victim%20does%20get%20an%20attorney%2C%20it%20takes%20several%20weeks%20for%20someone%20to%20take%20their%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20many%20people%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20legal%20counsel%2C%20victims%20often%20end%20up%20settling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20too%20many%20people%2C%20the%20best%20course%20of%20action%20is%20to%20keep%20their%20mouth%20shut%20and%20leave%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Utah%20State%20University%20business%20professor%20Susan%20Madsen%2C%20who%20helped%20launch%20A%20Bolder%20Way%20Forward.%20%26quot%3BThey%20just%20leave%20because%20they're%20not%20believed.%20They%20don't%20believe%20they'll%20be%20supported%20in%20their%20companies.%20It%20shouldn't%20be%20the%20best%20course%20of%20action%20for%20anyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernhardt%20said%20that%20the%20biggest%20pushback%20was%20in%20regard%20to%20how%20this%20bill%20would%20impact%20settlement%20agreements.%20It%20led%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fle.utah.gov%2F~2024%2Fpamend%2Fhb0055s02.sca.02.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20amendment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20states%20an%20employee%20may%20withdraw%20from%20a%20settlement%20agreement%20within%20three%20business%20days%20after%20they%20agreed%20to%20that%20settlement%20with%20a%20confidentiality%20clause%20regarding%20sexual%20misconduct.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20bullying%20tactics%20that%20go%20into%20the%20negotiations%20of%20these%20types%20of%20settlements%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernhardt%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20victims%20are%20left%20with%20a%20small%20window%20of%20time%20to%20accept%20an%20offer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20tip%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Armchan%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ermchan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%2C%20Signal%20at%20646.376.6106%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eor%20Telegram%20at%20%40rosaliechan.%C2%A0(PR%20pitches%20by%20email%20only%2C%20please.)%20Other%20types%20of%20secure%20messaging%20available%20upon%20request.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Futah-bill-nda-sexual-assault-harassment-unenforceable-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708133195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cff61aa610a9069d5a39de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Futah-bill-nda-sexual-assault-harassment-unenforceable-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bill%20makes%20confidentiality%20clauses%20about%20sexual%20assault%20and%20harassment%20unenforceable%2C%20impacting%20workplace%20culture%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rmchan%40businessinsider.com%20(Rosalie%20Chan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Futah-bill-nda-sexual-assault-harassment-unenforceable-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Budget%20carrier%20SpiceJet's%20MD%20Ajay%20Singh%20submits%20bid%20for%20bankrupt%20Go%20Fir