-verdict-whats-in-judge-engorons-decision-2024-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTrump%252C%2520his%2520eldest%2520sons%252C%2520and%2Cconscience%252C%2522%2520the%2520judge%2520wrote.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24364%20million%20verdict.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20she%20took%20a%20victory%20lap%2C%20calling%20the%20verdict%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20just%20for%20her%20state%2C%20but%20for%20%26quot%3Bevery%20American%26quot%3B%20who%20believes%20in%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20we%20proved%20that%20no%20one%20is%20above%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20remarks%20following%20the%20verdict.%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20how%20rich%2C%20powerful%2C%20or%20politically%20connected%20you%20are.%20Everyone%20must%20play%20by%20the%20same%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20for%20years%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20engaged%20in%20deceptive%20business%20practices.%20And%20tremendous%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued%2C%20repeating%20the%20judge's%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20falsely%2C%20knowingly%2C%20inflated%20his%20net%20worth%20by%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20unjustly%20enrich%20himself%2C%20his%20family%2C%20and%20to%20cheat%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20may%20have%20authored%20'The%20Art%20of%20the%20Deal%2C'%20she%20added%2C%20repeating%20a%20punchline%20from%20her%20September%202022%20announcement%20that%20she%20had%20sued%20Trump%20over%20his%20frauds.%20%26quot%3BBut%20he%20perfected%20'The%20Art%20of%20the%20Steal.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fag.ny.gov%2Fattorney-general-james-wins-landmark-victory-case-against-donald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWatch%20Letitia%20James'%20statement%20here.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20cash%20penalty%2C%20%24355%20million%20must%20be%20paid%20by%20Trump%20himself%2C%20with%20interest%20adding%20another%20%24100%20million%20more%20to%20