d%20all%20its%20three%20candidates%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Even%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20two%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20the%20party%20will%20be%20one%20vote%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lone%20BSP%20MLA%20Uma%20Shankar%20Singh%20has%20not%20made%20his%20inclinations%20clear%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20to%20take%20on%20sitting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsonia-gandhi-moves-to-rajya-sabha-as-congress-names-8-candidates-for-upper-house-polls%5C%22%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Mahajan%20who%20was%20considered%20close%20to%20former%20chief%20minister%20Virbhadra%20Singh%20left%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%202022.%20The%20Congress%20has%2040%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20assembly%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%2025%20and%203%20are%20independent%20MLAs.%20The%20saffron%20party%20is%20hoping%20that%20cross%20voting%20may%20help%20get%20Mahajan%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20high%20chance%20of%20cross-voting%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fbanking-on-discontent-within-the-ruling-congress-bjp-fields-a-rajya-sabha-candidate-from-himachal-pradesh%2Farticle67849015.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinghvi%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20from%20the%20state%20has%20upset%20a%20section%20of%20the%20party%2C%20after%20he%20was%20chosen%20over%20former%20union%20minister%20Anand%20Sharma%2C%20a%20party%20veteran%20from%20the%20state.%20Singhvi%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20is%20the%20first%20since%201952%20that%20a%20non-Himachali%20has%20been%20nominated%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%20from%20the%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20close%20to%20Anand%20Sharma%20said%20that%20lawmakers%20close%20to%20him%20are%20upset%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fhimachal%2Fhimachal-rs-nomination-anand-sharma-deeply-upset-keeps-cards-close-to-chest-591071%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20has%20fielded%20D.%20Kupendra%20Reddy%20on%20Thursday.%20Reddy%20is%20a%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20national%20president%20and%20national%20leaders%20and%20BJP%20state%20leaders%20joined%20together%20and%20ultimately%20we%20decided%20to%20file%20the%20nomination%20paper%20as%20an%20NDA%20candidate.%20JDS-BJP%20coalition%20candidate%2C%20Kupendra%20Reddy%20we%20selected%20from%20both%20the%20party%E2%80%A6We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20waste%20the%20votes%20for%20that%20reason%20Delhi%20high%20command%20also%20BJP%20high%20command%20advised%20us%20to%20put%20a%20candidate%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20file%20the%20nomination%20papers%20by%20Kupendra%20Reddy%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20JD(S)%20state%20president%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20to%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20in%20the%20state%20can%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%20with%20five%20candidates%20vying%20for%20four%20seats%20which%20are%20up%20for%20grabs.%20The%20Congress%20earlier%20named%20three%20candidates%20including%20Ajay%20Maken%2C%20G.C.%20Chandrashekhar%20and%20Syed%20Nasir%20Hussain.%20The%20BJP%20too%20earlier%20named%20Narayansa%20Bhandage%20as%20its%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20135%20MLAs%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%2066%20and%20the%20JD(S)%2019%20MLAs%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty-six%20seats%20spread%20across%2015%20states%20will%20be%20filled%20up%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20February%2027.%20Among%20those%20retiring%20are%2028%20MPs%20from%20the%20BJP%3B%2011%20from%20the%20Congress%3B%20four%20from%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%3B%20four%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%3B%20two%20each%20from%20the%20BJD%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%3B%20and%20one%20each%20from%20the%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20Sikkim%20Democratic%20Front.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708091081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16190716%2FEffect-2024-02-16T190700.306.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwith-new-nda-candidates-close-rajya-sabha-contest-likely-in-up-himachal-karnataka%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20named%20Sanjay%20Seth%20and%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20respectively%2C%20while%20JD(S)%2C%20BJP's%20ally%2C%20named%20D.%20Kupendra%20Reddy%20from%20Karnataka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwith-new-nda-candidates-close-rajya-sabha-contest-likely-in-up-himachal-karnataka%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Grow%20Water%20Lilies%20at%20Home%3F%20Tips%20From%20Homemaker%20Who%20Earns%20Rs%201%20Lakh%2FMonth%20Selling%20Them%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20finishing%20her%20household%20chores%2C%20what%20Viji%20Abi%20eagerly%20anticipates%20in%20her%20daily%20routine%20is%20caring%20for%20her%20home%20garden%20and%20engaging%20with%20her%20gardening%20friends%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20entering%20her%20garden%20in%20Thrissur%2C%20Kerala%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20welcomed%20by%20a%20vibrant%20display%20of%20blooming%20flowers.%20However%2C%20the%20standout%20feature%20of%20the%20garden%20is%20her%20water%20lily%20pots%20containing%20exotic-coloured%20lilies.%20As%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20few%20water%20lily%20hybridisers%2C%20Viji%E2%80%99s%20garden%20proudly%20showcases%20a%20hybrid%20variety%20she%20cultivated%20called%20Nymphaea%20Sree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGardening%20started%20as%20a%20leisure%20activity%20but%20transformed%20into%20my%20passion.%20I%20was%20inquisitive%20about%20how%20lily%20plants%20are%20grown%20and%20which%20variety%20survives.%20Now%2C%20I%20earn%20more%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh%20a%20month%20by%20selling%20lilies%20during%20a%20good%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViji%20shares%20the%20secrets%20behind%20her%20healthy%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F208990%2Fsustainable-garden-green-peace-home-garden-indoor-plants-garden-workshops-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreen%20garden%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20how%20you%20too%20can%20grow%20water%20lilies%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJourney%20to%20her%20magic%20garden%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20with%20an%20affinity%20for%20plants%20and%20greenery%2C%20Viji%20has%20been%20fond%20of%20gardening%20for%20most%20of%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20must%20have%20been%20decades%20since%20I%20have%20been%20tending%20to%20a%20garden.%20It%20is%20my%20favourite%20thing%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20becoming%20a%20full-time%20gardener%2C%20she%20was%20an%20accountant.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20sounds%20like%20two%20different%20worlds%2C%20but%20for%20me%2C%20gardening%20was%20always%20a%20part%20of%20who%20I%20was.%20When%20my%20first%20child%20was%20born%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20lived%20on%20our%20own.%20So%20one%20of%20us%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313207%2Faravinthan-coimbatore-organic-farm-seed-bank-preserves-rare-varieties-vegetables-pulses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equit%20our%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20raise%20the%20children.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20my%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20putting%20down%20her%20papers%2C%20Viji%E2%80%99s%20mind%20was%20not%20at%20ease.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20create%20and%20leave%20back%20something%20of%20my%20own%20in%20the%20world.%20But%2C%20I%20did%20not%20have%20the%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20with%20the%20birth%20of%20her%20newborn%2C%20the%20young%20mother%20started%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20her%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CTending%20the%20baby%20and%20the%20garden%20gave%20me%20solace%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-5-1708088457.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Viji%20grows%20over%20100%20varieties%20of%20lilies%20in%20her%20garden.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-5-1708088457.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-5-1708088457-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-5-1708088457-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-5-1708088457-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-5-1708088457-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342128%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EViji%20grows%20over%20100%20varieties%20of%20lilies%20in%20her%20garden.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViji%E2%80%99s%20gardening%20journey%20started%20with%20growing%20bougainvillaeas%2C%20orchids%20and%20roses.%20She%20adds%20that%20she%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20flowers%20in%20her%20garden%2C%20and%20she%20even%3Ca%20rel%3D%5