%20nutrients%20for%20farmers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20Best%20Dosa%20Places%20in%20Chennai%20That%20Also%20Serve%20Epic%20South%20Indian%20Thalis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20map%20of%20decadent%20fine-dining%20restaurants%20on%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20bustling%20streets%20is%20interspersed%20with%20traditional%20hole-in-the-wall%20eateries.%20These%20usually%20cater%20to%20two%20palates%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20delights%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333205%2Fprasanna-karthik-viral-tweet-idli-in-tadka-restaurant-in-japan-for-south-indian-breakfast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20Indian%20breakfasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20other%20that%20takes%20pleasure%20in%20meaty%20main%20courses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vibrant%20city%20takes%20great%20pride%20in%20its%20gastronomy%20and%20has%20enjoyed%20breathless%20coverage%20of%20its%20military-era%20hotels.%20And%20history%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20their%20inception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20goes%20that%20it%20was%20during%20World%20War%20II%20that%20these%20military%20outlets%20mushroomed%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20satisfy%20the%20troops%E2%80%99%20hunger.%20Now%2C%20neither%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20newer%20Chettinad%20restaurants%20nor%20the%20glam%20of%20the%20fine-dining%20spots%20can%20dim%20the%20allure%20that%20military%20hotels%20continue%20to%20retain%20in%20the%20city.%20From%20politicians%20to%20the%20who%E2%80%99s%20who%20of%20Southern%20cinema%2C%20everyone%20has%20stopped%20here%20for%20a%20bite%20and%20has%20a%20story%20to%20tell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20we%20chronicle%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20best%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F264506%2Fnew-